## 컴포넌트 프리셋(권장 Tailwind 클래스)
- PageRoot: `min-h-dvh bg-dq-charcoalDeep text-dq-white`
- Panel: `bg-dq-charcoal border border-white/10 rounded-2xl`
- SubPanel: `bg-dq-black border border-white/10 rounded-2xl`
- Divider: `border-t border-white/10`
- Badge(중립): `bg-white/10 text-white/80 rounded-full px-2 py-0.5 text-xs`
- Badge(강조): `bg-dq-red/15 text-dq-white ring-1 ring-dq-redLight/60`
- PrimaryButton:
  - base: `h-14 px-5 rounded-2xl bg-dq-red text-dq-white font-bold`
  - disabled: `disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed`
  - focus: `focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-dq-redLight focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-dq-charcoalDeep`
- SecondaryButton:
  - `h-14 px-5 rounded-2xl bg-white/10 text-dq-white border border-white/10`
- Chip(팀 표시):
  - base: `size-10 rounded-full grid place-items-center border-2`
  - team red/blue/green은 `border-dq-*/ bg-dq-*/` 조합 (패턴/아이콘 병행)

## 타이포(권장)
- 한글/UI: Noto Sans KR
- 라틴/숫자: Inter
- 룸 코드/로그(고정폭): JetBrains Mono(또는 `font-mono`)
- 타입 스케일(권장)
  - Display: 32~40px
  - Heading: 18~24px
  - Body: 14~16px
  - Caption: 12~13px

## 접근성/터치
- 버튼/터치 타겟: 44px 이상
- 키보드 포커스: `focus-visible` 링 필수
- iOS Safari / Android Chrome 최신 2개 메이저 지원
